sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Plugin
    participant GW as AI-Gateway

    P->>GW: WebSocket 连接 (auth. subprotocol)
    Note over GW: AK/SK 签名验证
    GW-->>P: 连接建立
    Note over GW: 启动 register 超时计时器 (10s)

    P->>GW: register 消息
    Note over GW: 设备绑定校验 + 重复连接检查
    alt 注册成功
        GW-->>P: register_ok
        Note over P: 状态 → READY, 启动心跳
    else 注册失败
        GW-->>P: register_rejected
        GW->>P: 关闭连接 (4403/4409)
    end

    loop 每 heartbeatIntervalMs
        P->>GW: heartbeat
        Note over GW: 更新 last_seen_at
    end

    Note over P: 断开时
    GW->>GW: markOffline + 通知 Skill Server agent_offline
